## About the Book

These examples come from **"Advanced Functional Programming with Elixir"** published by [The Pragmatic Bookshelf](https://pragprog.com/titles/jkelixir/advanced-functional-programming-with-elixir).

The book provides the complete explanations, theory, and context for these examples. The notebooks let you run and experiment with the concepts hands-on.

